\begin_body

\begin_layout Paragraph
MA141(初中竞赛, 初等数论)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Determine all sets consisting of an odd number 
\begin_inset Formula $2m+1$
\end_inset

 of consecutive positive integers, for some integer 
\begin_inset Formula $m\geq1$
\end_inset

 such that the sum of the cubes of the smallest 
\begin_inset Formula $m+1$
\end_inset

 integers is equal to the sum of the cubes of the largest 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 integers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
MA142(几何, 小学数学, 面积相等的证明, 列方程法)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The sketch shown is from the files of Leonardo da Vinci.
 Two perpendicular diameters divide a circle into four parts.
 On each of these diameters a circle of half the diameter is drawn, tangent
 to the original circle and meeting at its centre.
 A radius to the large circle is drawn through the intersection points of
 these smaller circles.
 Show that the red and blue shaded regions are of the same area.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename pics/area-1.png

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
MA143
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The integers from 1 to 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 are added to form the sum 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

 and the integers from 1 to 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 are added to form the sum 
\begin_inset Formula $M$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $n>m+1$
\end_inset

.
 If the difference between the two sums is 
\begin_inset Formula $N-M=2012$
\end_inset

, then determine the value of 
\begin_inset Formula $n+m$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
MA144
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Betty和Greta在一张
\begin_inset Formula $7\times7$
\end_inset

的棋盘上玩一个游戏, Betty先走.
 Betty每走一步, 都在棋盘上找到一个未经涂色的
\begin_inset Formula $2\times2$
\end_inset

的区块将其涂成棕色.
 Greta每走一步都在棋盘上选择一个未经涂色的格子将其涂成绿色.
 当Betty没有区块可以涂色时, 剩下的格子由Greta全部涂成绿色.
 试问, 是否有哪个选手有必胜策略, 无论对手怎么操作, 自己涂色的数量总能至少染色
\begin_inset Formula $25$
\end_inset

个方格.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Ans
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
考虑在方格棋盘上, 坐标都为偶数的
\begin_inset Formula $9$
\end_inset

个格子.
 Betty的每一步染色必然覆盖这
\begin_inset Formula $9$
\end_inset

个格子中的其中一个, 而且每个格子对应一种
\begin_inset Formula $2\times2$
\end_inset

的填充方式.
 如果Greta无论先手还是后手, 先占据
\begin_inset Formula $9$
\end_inset

个格子中的
\begin_inset Formula $4$
\end_inset

个, 则Betty最多只能走
\begin_inset Formula $5$
\end_inset

步, 也只能染色
\begin_inset Formula $20$
\end_inset

个方格.
 所以Greta有必胜策略.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
MA145(数论, 初等数论, 整除)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Determine all integers 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 for which 
\begin_inset Formula $n^{3}-3n+2$
\end_inset

 is divisible by 
\begin_inset Formula $2n+1$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
OC552(数论, 解方程)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $a,b$
\end_inset

为两个不同的正实数, 考虑方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lfloor ax+b\rfloor=\lfloor bx+a\rfloor,
\]

\end_inset

证明: 存在一个区间长度至少为
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{\max\left\{ a,b\right\} }$
\end_inset

的区间, 使得区间内的每个值都是上述方程的解.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
不妨设
\begin_inset Formula $a\ge b$
\end_inset

, 记
\begin_inset Formula $a+b=n+r$
\end_inset

, 其中
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

是整数, 
\begin_inset Formula $0\le r<1$
\end_inset

, 则区间
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\frac{a-r}{a},\frac{1+a-r}{a}\right)$
\end_inset

内的每个点都满足方程.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
OC553(数论, 整数)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求所有的整数数对
\begin_inset Formula $(a,b)$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $a^{2}+2b^{2}+2a+1$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $2ab$
\end_inset

的一个因子.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
OC555(数论, 2018 Poland MO, 6th problem, final round)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $p>3$
\end_inset

为素数, 
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

是满足下式的
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ 1,2,\cdots,p\right\} $
\end_inset

的置换
\begin_inset Formula $(a_{1},a_{2},\cdots,a_{p})$
\end_inset

的总数, 使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p\mid a_{1}a_{2}+a_{2}a_{3}+\cdots+a_{p-1}a_{p}+a_{p}a_{1},
\]

\end_inset

证明: 
\begin_inset Formula $p^{2}\mid K+p$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
定义: 
\begin_inset Formula $d:\left(\mathbb{F}_{p}\right)^{d}\to\left(\mathbb{F}_{p}\right)^{d}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $v:\left(\mathbb{F}_{p}\right)^{d}\to\mathbb{F}_{p}$
\end_inset

, 如下:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}d\left(x_{1},x_{2},\ldots,x_{p}\right) & =\left(x_{2}-x_{1},x_{3}-x_{2},\ldots,x_{p}-x_{p-1},x_{1}-x_{p}\right)\\
v\left(x_{1},x_{2}\ldots,x_{p}\right) & =x_{1}x_{2}+x_{2}x_{3}+\cdots+x_{p-1}x_{p}+x_{p}x_{1}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

再定义, 滑移
\begin_inset Formula $\ell_{h}:(\mathbb{F}_{p})^{p}\to(\mathbb{F}_{p})^{p}$
\end_inset

, 提升
\begin_inset Formula $s_{h}:(\mathbb{F}_{p})^{p}\to(\mathbb{F}_{p})^{p}$
\end_inset

如下:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\ell_{h}\left(x_{1},x_{2},\ldots,x_{p}\right) & =\left(x_{1}+h,x_{2}+h,\ldots,x_{p}+h\right)\\
s_{h}\left(x_{1},x_{2},\ldots,x_{p}\right) & =\left(x_{1+h},x_{2+h},\ldots,x_{p+h}\right)
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

则有, 对于任意的
\begin_inset Formula $X\in(\mathbb{F}_{p})^{p}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\ell_{1}(s_{1}(X))=s_{1}(\ell_{1}(X))$
\end_inset

, 故
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\ell_{h_{1}}\circ s_{k_{1}}\circ\ell_{h_{2}}\circ s_{k_{2}}\cdots\ell_{h_{n}}\circ s_{k_{n}}(X) & =\ell_{h_{1}+h_{2}+\cdots+h_{n}}\left(s_{k_{1}+k_{2}+\cdots+k_{n}}(X)\right)\\
 & =s_{k_{1}+k_{2}+\cdots+k_{n}}\left(\ell_{h_{1}+h_{2}+\cdots+h_{n}}(X)\right).
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

对于
\begin_inset Formula $X,Y\in(\mathbb{F}_{p})^{p}$
\end_inset

, 记
\begin_inset Formula $X\sim Y$
\end_inset

, 如果存在某个
\begin_inset Formula $h$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula $Y=s_{h}(X)$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\sim$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $(\mathbb{F}_{p})^{p}$
\end_inset

上的一个等价关系.
 设
\begin_inset Formula $\pi,\rho$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{F}_{p}$
\end_inset

上的置换, 记
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\approx\rho$
\end_inset

, 如果
\begin_inset Formula $d(\pi)\sim d(\rho)$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\approx$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{F}_{p}$
\end_inset

的置换集合
\begin_inset Formula $S_{p}$
\end_inset

上的一个等价关系.
 且有关系
\begin_inset Formula $d(\ell_{i}(\pi))=d(\pi)$
\end_inset

, 所以每个
\begin_inset Formula $\pi$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

个与之等价的滑移.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于任意的
\begin_inset Formula $h,k\in\mathbb{F}_{p}$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula $\ell_{h}(\pi)\approx\pi\approx s_{k}(\pi)$
\end_inset

, 因此
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\approx s_{k}(\ell_{h}(\pi))$
\end_inset

, 即等价类
\begin_inset Formula $\left[\pi\right]_{\approx}$
\end_inset

是所有
\begin_inset Formula $\pi$
\end_inset

通过连续的提升与滑移所得的所有置换集合.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于
\begin_inset Formula $\pi=(a_{1},\cdots,a_{p})$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v\left(\ell_{1}(\pi)\right)=\sum_{k=1}^{p}\left(a_{k}+1\right)\left(a_{k+1}+1\right)=v(\pi)+p^{2}=v(\pi)+0=v(\pi).
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $[\pi]_{\approx}$
\end_inset

下是良定的, 也就是当
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\approx\rho$
\end_inset

时, 有
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

使得
\begin_inset Formula $\ell_{i}(\pi)=\rho$
\end_inset

, 从而
\begin_inset Formula $v(\pi)=v(\rho)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于
\begin_inset Formula $1\le m\le p-1$
\end_inset

, 考虑置换
\begin_inset Formula $\pi_{m}=(0,m,2m,3m,\cdots,(p-1)m)$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi_{m}$
\end_inset

的等价类
\begin_inset Formula $[\pi_{m}]_{\approx}$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

个元素, (对应
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

个滑移, 但提升保持
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

值, 即
\begin_inset Formula $d(s_{i}(\pi))=d(\pi)$
\end_inset

), 且
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v(\pi_{m})=m\sum_{k=0}^{p-1}k(k+1)=0,
\]

\end_inset

只需考虑
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\not\in\bigcup_{m=1}^{p-1}[\pi_{m}]_{\approx}$
\end_inset

, 由于
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

是素数, 故
\begin_inset Formula $d(s_{0}(\pi))$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $d(s_{1}(\pi))$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\cdots$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $d(s_{p-1}(\pi))$
\end_inset

两两不同.
 否则, 不妨设
\begin_inset Formula $d(s_{i}(\pi))=d(s_{j}(\pi))$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $i>j$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $i,j\in\mathbb{Z}_{p}$
\end_inset

, 则由定义, 
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{k+i+1}-x_{k+i})_{k=1}^{p}=(x_{k+j+1}-x_{k+j})_{k=1}^{p}$
\end_inset

, 比如
\begin_inset Formula $k=p$
\end_inset

时对应等式
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i+2}-x_{i+1}=x_{j+2}-x_{j+1}$
\end_inset

.
 若记
\begin_inset Formula $d=i-j$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{k}=x_{j+2+kd}-x_{j+1+kd}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $y_{1}=y_{0}$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula $y_{k+1}=y_{k}$
\end_inset

.
 由于
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

是素数, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(j+2+kd\right)_{k=1}^{p}$
\end_inset

刚好取遍
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{Z}_{p}$
\end_inset

, 而这说明
\begin_inset Formula $y_{k}$
\end_inset

作为
\begin_inset Formula $x_{k}$
\end_inset

相邻两项的差分总是常数, 这与
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\not\in\bigcup_{m=1}^{p-1}[\pi_{m}]_{\approx}$
\end_inset

矛盾.
 故
\begin_inset Formula $[\pi]_{\approx}$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula $p^{2}$
\end_inset

个元素, 若这些等价类中有
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

个的
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

值为
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

, 则满足
\begin_inset Formula $v(\pi)=0$
\end_inset

的所有的
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\in S_{p}$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula $(p-1)p+Cp^{2}$
\end_inset

个, 即得所求的结果.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
使用Conway三角形记号求解代数问题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Conway坐标
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $x,y,z\in\RR$
\end_inset

满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x+y>0;y+z>0;z+x>0;xy+yz+zx>0;
\]

\end_inset

记
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a=\sqrt{x+y},\ b=\sqrt{y+z},\ c=\sqrt{z+x},
\]

\end_inset

则
\begin_inset Formula $a,b,c$
\end_inset

是某个非退化三角形的三边长, 即
\begin_inset Formula $a+b>c$
\end_inset

.
 三角形的半周长和面积为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
s=\frac{1}{2}\left(\sqrt{x+y}+\sqrt{y+z}+\sqrt{z+x}\right),\quad S=\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{xy+yz+zx}.
\]

\end_inset

三角形对应的内接圆半径
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

与外接圆半径
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r=\frac{S}{C}=\frac{\sqrt{xy+yz+zx}}{\sqrt{x+y}+\sqrt{y+z}+\sqrt{z+x}},\quad R=\frac{abc}{4F}=\frac{\sqrt{(x+y)(y+z)(z+x)}}{2\sqrt{xy+yz+zx}}
\]

\end_inset

三角形中线长公式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m_{a}^{2}=\frac{x+y+4z}{4};\quad m_{b}^{2}=\frac{4x+y+z}{4};\quad m_{c}^{2}=\frac{x+4y+z}{4}.
\]

\end_inset

三角形的高线长为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
h_{a} & =\sqrt{\frac{xy+yz+zx}{x+y}}=\sqrt{z+\frac{xy}{x+y}},\\
h_{b} & =\sqrt{\frac{xy+yz+zx}{y+z}}=\sqrt{x+\frac{yz}{y+z}},\\
h_{c} & =\sqrt{\frac{xy+yz+zx}{z+x}}=\sqrt{y+\frac{zx}{z+x}},
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Ex 1.
 (Turkey NMO - 2006)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $x,y,z>0$
\end_inset

, 满足
\begin_inset Formula $xy+yz+zx=1$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{27}{4}(x+y)(y+z)(z+x)\geq(\sqrt{x+y}+\sqrt{y+z}+\sqrt{z+x})^{2}\geq6\sqrt{3}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
pf
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
相当于证明
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{27}{4}a^{2}b^{2}c^{2}\geq(a+b+c)^{2}
\]

\end_inset

代入
\begin_inset Formula $R=\frac{abc}{4S}=\frac{abc}{2}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $2s=a+b+c$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula $27R^{2}\ge4s^{2}$
\end_inset

.
 这等价于Mitrinovi
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
'{c}
\end_layout

\end_inset

不等式.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
第二个不等式相当于证明, 
\begin_inset Formula $s^{2}\ge\frac{3}{2}\sqrt{3}$
\end_inset

.
 由于
\begin_inset Formula $S=rs=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

, 所以等价于证明
\begin_inset Formula $s^{2}\ge3\sqrt{3}rs$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula $s\ge3\sqrt{3}r$
\end_inset

, 这又等价于Mitrinovi
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


